# 副簽
(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺文件、信件或者網頁上面，主簽名（或者主要簽署人）下面嘅額外簽名（量詞：個）
eng:co-signature; counter-signature
<eg>
yue:呢份合約需要經理同財務總監一齊簽名，所以經理嘅簽名下面要有財務總監嘅副簽。 (ni1 fan2 haap3 jyu6 mui4 ging1 gei3 cou4 wui6 caam1 sai1, so2 ji5 ging1 gei3 gei3 sai1 haahm6 min5 jau6 wui6 cou4 wui6 caam1 gei3 gei3 fu6 sai1.)
eng:The contract requires both the manager and the finance director to sign, so there must be the finance director's co-signature below the manager's signature. [end of text]


